The paper focuses on the problem of face verification using deep neural networks, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The study also involves evaluating the performance of different models on large-scale datasets, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with the effects of covariates on face verification, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR).
